quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,10,jo log kafir hue ( is din ) nah to un ka maal hi khuda ( ke azaab ) se un ko bacha sakay ga aur nah un ki aulaad hi ( kuch kaam aeye gi ) aur yeh log aatish ( jahannum ) ka eendhan hon ge
  3,11,un ka haal bhi firounion aur un se pehlay logon ka sa hoga jinhon ne hamari aayton ki takzieeb ki thi to khuda ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab ( azaab mein ) pakar liya tha aur khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
  3,12,( ae paighambar ) kafiroon se kehdo ke tum ( duniya mein bhi ) anqareeb maghloob ho jao ge aur ( akhirat mein ) jahannum ki taraf hankay jao ge aur woh buri jagah hai
  3,13,tumahray liye do garohoon mein jo ( jung badar ke din ) aapas mein bhir gay ( qudrat khuda ki azeem al shan ) nishani thi aik giroh ( musalmanoon ka tha woh ) khuda ki raah mein lar raha tha aur dosra giroh ( kafiroon ka tha woh ) un ko apni aankhon se apne se dugna mushahida kar raha tha aur khuda apni nusrat se jis ko chahta hai madad deta hai jo ahal Basarat hain un ke liye is ( waqeye ) mein barri Ibrat hai
  3,14,logon ko un ki khawahishon ki cheeze yani aurtain aur betay aur sonay aur chandi ke barray barray dhair aur nishaan lagey hue ghoray aur maweshi aur khaiti barri zeenat daar maloom hoti hain ( magar ) yeh sab duniya hi ki zindagi ke samaan hain aur khuda ke paas bohat acha thikana hai
  3,15,( ae paighambar un se ) kaho ke bhala mein tum ko aisi cheez batau jo un cheezon se kahin achi ho ( suno ) jo log parhaizgaar hain un ke liye khuda ke haan baagaat ( bahisht ) hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain un mein woh hamesha rahen ge aur pakeeza aurtain hain aur ( sab se barh kar ) khuda ki khushnodi aur khuda ( apne naik ) bundon ko dekh raha hai
